reviews.review_text: richmond va Thanks Tony Suraci for this download, I believe I patched into with my Nac 550. I  really cranked up the level when recording. The new Minglewood is killer.. Phil dropin large bombs. Sure its me,was there, but its a great show,see if I can figure out how to upload to contribute..
Post-drums... The post-drums segues from space -> Throwin' Stones -> GDTRFB -> Saturday Night are really sweet here!  Suraci's uploads from this tour really sound sweet, too!
